Sentencas: The use of a dense film to modify perovskite is a new approach to develop highly stable cathode for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: A (La,Sr)MnO3 nano-film embedded into (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 porous cathode for stability enhancement

Sentencas: Here, we report that La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 (LSMO) surface decoration led to markedly enhanced stability and activity of conventional Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF).
Titulo: A (La,Sr)MnO3 nano-film embedded into (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 porous cathode for stability enhancement

Sentencas: This novel cathode architecture has a potential to make effective use of the desirable properties of two different materials: the high oxygen ionic conductivity of a BSCF backbone and the excellent stability and high catalytic activity of an LSMO film-coating.
Titulo: A (La,Sr)MnO3 nano-film embedded into (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 porous cathode for stability enhancement

Sentencas: An optimized impregnation technology was used to prepare a uniform and continuous LSMO nano-film into BSCF porous cathode.
Titulo: A (La,Sr)MnO3 nano-film embedded into (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 porous cathode for stability enhancement
